'S e aon de na h-[[Eileanan a' Chaolais]] a th’ ann an '''Crevichon'''. 

Tha e suidhichte anns a’ [[Caolas Sasannach|Chaolas Shasannach]] san taobh tuath  [[Jethou]] agus faisg air [[Herm]].

Tha e na phàirt den [[Guernsey|Bailiwick of Guernsey]].

Bha cuaraidh clach ghraineil air an eilean, canar gun tàinig clachan na staidhre St Paul's Cathedral ann an [[Lunnainn]] à Crevichon. <ref> [http://www.telegraph.co.uk/portal/main.jhtml?xml=/portal/exclusions/quiteinteresting/nosplit/ftqi118.xml  The Daily Telegraph, 2007-08-18]</ref>
